result.execSummary:
The defendant Jennifer A. Forster was found guilty of the following charge(s) in this case. One or more other charges in this case were dismissed. The dismissed charges were not proven and have no legal effect. Jennifer A. Forster is presumed innocent of the dismissed charges.

  • Jennifer A. Forster was found guilty of Disorderly Conduct, a class B misdemeanor, Wisconsin Statutes 947.01(1).
